<i>noun</i>: 폭압 [포갑], 평정 [평정], 진압 [지ː납], 억제 [억쩨] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>폭압 [포갑]</dt><br>
<dd>oppression; coercion; repression</dd><br>
<dd>폭력을 써서 억지로 누름.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of putting pressure on someone or a group of people, using violence.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>평정 [평정]</dt><br>
<dd>1. suppression; repression</dd><br>
<dd>반란이나 폭동 등을 누르고 조용하고 편안한 상태로 만듦.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of suppressing a rebellion, riot, etc., and making a quiet and peaceful state.</dd><br>
<dd>2. subjugation</dd><br>
<dd>적을 쳐서 자신의 지배 아래 놓이게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of defeating an enemy and putting them under one’s control.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>진압 [지ː납]</dt><br>
<dd>suppression; repression</dd><br>
<dd>강제로 억눌러 진정시킴.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of putting down by force.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>억제 [억쩨]</dt><br>
<dd>1. suppression; control; repression</dd><br>
<dd>감정이나 욕망, 충동적 행동 등을 내리눌러서 일어나지 못하게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of suppressing feelings, desires, impulses, etc., to stop them from occurring.</dd><br>
<dd>2. control; restraint; suppression</dd><br>
<dd>정도나 한도를 넘어서 나아가려는 것을 억눌러 멈추게 함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of suppressing something to stop it from exceeding a level or limit.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>